log
@Obvious .Xr fixes, found while testing mandocdb(8).
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: getmntinfo.3,v 1.12 2013/06/05 03:39:22 tedu Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1989, 1991, 1993
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
